# CODEOWNERS
# 
# This file defines code ownership for the hve-core repository.
# Code owners are automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull request
# that modifies files they own.
#
# Syntax: <file-pattern> @owner1 @owner2
# More info: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# GitHub Actions workflows require approval from any repository collaborator with write access
# This ensures security-sensitive workflow changes are reviewed by trusted maintainers
# Note: * means any repository collaborator with write access (portable across organizations)
/.github/workflows/ *

# Security automation scripts require approval from any repository collaborator with write access
# Note: * means any repository collaborator with write access (portable across organizations)
/scripts/security/ *
